text:
Hi Superpathers! (If that's what you're called :D) I'm Renae, Content Marketing Writer at CloudFactory, a managed workforce provider for data processing, machine learning, and AI.

Before joining CloudFactory late last year, I ran my own freelance writing and editing practice for almost 20 years!

I love writing and editing, and creating awesome content that helps thought leaders get big bold ideas out of their heads, and into the world, influencing and selling for them.

Look forward to learning from and with you all! I love connecting with other content marketers and writers, so I welcome connections on <https://www.linkedin.com/in/renaegregoire/|LinkedIn> and <http://twitter.com/writerren|Twitter>.

By the way, CloudFactory is hiring a full-time, B2B tech writer, fully remote. If you're interested in learning more, let me know!
